import styled from 'styled-components'
import Address from '../../components/signup/Address'
import Email from '../../components/signup/Email'
import Id from '../../components/signup/Id'
import Name from '../../components/signup/Name'
import Password from '../../components/signup/Password'
import PasswordCheck from '../../components/signup/PasswordCheck'
import Phone from '../../components/signup/Phone'
import Gender from '../../components/signup/Gender'
import Birth from '../../components/signup/Birth'

export default function Form() {
  return (
    <InputContainer>
      <Id />
      <Password />
      <PasswordCheck />
      <Name />
      <Email />
      <Phone />
      <Address />
      <Gender />
      <Birth />
    </InputContainer>
  )
}

const InputContainer = styled.div`
  padding: 0px;
`
